@node "GuiX_Premessa" "5.1 GuiX: Introduction"


 GuiX is the graphic user interface of xFX. This software is based on  Magic
User Interface (MUI, © Stefan Stunz) and was developed to simplfy as much as
possible the xFX use. It has built-in tools that allow  some  functions  not
implemented in xFX. In-line help and bubble help allow a very intuitive  use
of GuiX and xFX.

 Unlike some others graphic  interfaces,  GuiX  comunicates  bidirectionally
with  xFX  trough  ARexx  port.  This  comunication  method  allows  a  high
integration of these two programs.


Unlike xFX, GuiX need the KickStart 3.0 or better to work.
@endnode

