     |@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +---------+--+@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}    |             +-------------+---+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}   End |         |79|@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}    B             +-----------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
