     @{fg fill}|@{fg text}|        @{u}S@{uu}tart        | @{fg shine}|@{fg text}                  +--------------++-+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg text}+---------------------+ @{fg shine}+-------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|
     +-------------------------------------------------------------+-+
     |                                                             |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|
     +-------------------------------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}


 @{b}Description:@{ub}

@{fg shine}A) Listview of XPK compression methods.@{fg text}
 This list is disabled if the @{i}Pack@{ui} option (section B) is not checked. If do
you want use the GZip compression, this list is disabled.

@{fg shine}B) Optional functions.@{fg text}

 Cyclic gadget:
 XPK       ->  Activates XPK libraries to compress.
 GZip      ->  Uses GZip to compress.

 Checkboxes:
 Add Icon  ->  Adds an icon to file-disk.
 Pack      ->  Activates the file-disk compression.
 MontList  ->  Generates automatically the fmsdisk.device mountlist.
               (see @{" Shell use " link "Shell" 0})
 No Eject  ->  Inhibits the automatic disk ejection.

@{fg shine}C) Slider of XPK efficiency compression.@{fg text}
 This option is disabled if the @{i}Pack@{ui} option (section B) is not checked.

@{fg shine}D) XPK password (optional).@{fg text}
 This option is disabled if the @{i}Pack@{ui} option (section B) is not  checked.  It
allows to specify an encryption password if needed.

@{fg shine}E) Mountlist file to create.@{fg text}
 This item is not activated if the  Mountlist  option  (section  B)  is  not
checked.
@endnode

