 @{b}Description:@{ub}

@{fg shine}A) Verify checkbox.@{fg text}
 This checkbox activates the cylinder verification.

@{fg shine}B) No Eject checkbox.@{fg text}
 If checked, this option inhibits the automatic disk ejection.

@{fg shine}C) Password item (optional).@{fg text}
 If needed, in this string gadget you can specify a decryption password.
@endnode

