@node "GuiX_Checksum" "5.5.1 GuiX:  Checksum calculator"


 @{b}Short key: @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 1@{ub}@{fg text}

 This is a tool for  multiformat  calculation  of  file-disk  checksum.  The
supported method are five:

 Brick CRC-32  <-- It's the GNU command Brick
 BSD           <-- Without polinomial table
 MD5           <-- 64 bit with polinomial table
 Posix         <-- With polinomial table
 System V      <-- Without polinomial table


  @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} CheckSum Calculator     @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +----------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}  File |                ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}| @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- File name for calculation
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +----------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +--+----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{u}@{fg text}M@{uu}ethod ||^|  Brick CRC-32  | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Method
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}       +--+----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+---------- Checksum ---------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Dec @{fg shine}-@{fg text}                       @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Decimal checksum
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Hex @{fg shine}-@{fg text}                       @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Hexadecimal checksum
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+----------+    +----------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|   C@{u}a@{uu}lc   |    |  @{u}C@{uu}ancel  | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Control buttons:
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+----------+    +----------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}     Calc   = calculates the checksum
  @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}     Cancel = closes the window
  @{fg fill}+-----------------------------+-+@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}|                             |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
  @{fg fill}+-----------------------------+-+@{fg text}

  Menu items:

  @{b}Checksum@{ub}
    Calculate   <-- Activates the calculation (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + C@{fg text})
    ---------
    Close       <-- Closes the window (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + Q@{fg text})
@endnode

@node "GuiX_DizToolkit" "5.5.2 GuiX: Diz Toolkit"


 @{b}Short Key:@{ub} @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 2@{fg text}

 DizToolkit is a little utility to add, extract and  remove  comments  (diz)
from/to XPK packed file-disks.  At the end of file is added a text file with
special string markers.



 +---- File name
 |
 |
 |   @{fg fill}+-+-----------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} Diz Toolkit                       @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+-+-----------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------File-Disk--------+ +-----------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+--------------------++-+@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +-> @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|Ram:MyDisk.xfx      ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}|@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}|   @{u}N@{uu}ew   |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- @{"Add a comment" link "GuiX_DizToolkit_New" 0}
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+--------------------++-+@{fg shine}| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}+-------------------------+ |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}+-------FILE-ID.diz-------+ |@{fg text}| @{u}E@{uu}xtract |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Extract the comment
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|+---------------------+-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}FileType:@{ub}@{fg shine}            |@{fg text}*@{fg shine}|| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|
     |@{fg shine}||@{fg text}[NUKE] File-Disk@{fg shine}     | || |@{fg text}| @{u}R@{uu}emove  |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Remove the comment
     @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Name:@{ub}@{fg shine}                | || |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +-> @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{fg text}My Disk@{fg shine}              +-+| |           |@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Author:@{ub}@{fg shine}              |@{fg text}=@{fg shine}|| |           |@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{fg text}Alessandro Pedretti@{fg shine}  +-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}||@{b}@{fg text}Generated by:@{ub}@{fg shine}        |@{fg text}=@{fg shine}|| |@{fg text}|  @{u}C@{uu}lose  |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <-- Closes the window
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|+---------------------+-+| |@{fg text}+---------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-------------------------+ +-----------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+---------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}|                                       |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 |   @{fg fill}+---------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 |
 |
 +---- Comment description


