@node "GuiX_Splitter" "5.5.3 GuiX: File Splitter"


 @{b}Short key: @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 3@{ub}@{fg text}

 The File Splitter is a GuiX section that is able to split a file-disk  into
more  then  one  file  with  prefixed size. In this way, you can split  very
big files into more then one disks. File splitter is also  able  to  execute
the join operation to recreate the original file-disk, using a set of  files
with smaller size. You can also perform this operation  using  the  AmigaDOS
command JOIN.  All files generated from the original file-disk, have a  name
composed of a prefix specified by user and of  numerical suffix (extension),
like: PREFIX_NAME.001 The maximum number of splitted files is 999.



      Mode:
 +--- Split = creates a set of files from a file-disk
 |    Join  = joins all splitted files to create the original file-disk
 |
 | @{fg fill}+-+----------------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} File Splitter                          @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}+-+----------------------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+----------------- File-Disk ----------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +--------------------------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}      File name to  split
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Name |                                ||^| @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- or name of any file
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +--------------------------------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}      to join
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +--+---------+        +----------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +>@{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} @{u}M@{uu}ode ||^|  Split  | Prefix |          ||^| @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- File prefix
   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +--+---------+        +----------++-+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
   @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +------------+ +--+-----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 +>@{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} @{u}S@{uu}ize |            | ||^|     Custom      | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- Presetted sizes
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +------------+ +--+-----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} +-----------------+    +-----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} |     @{u}E@{uu}xecute     |    |     @{u}C@{uu}ancel      | @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- Closes the window
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} +-----------------+    +-----------------+ @{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------------------------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}+--------------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}|                                            |@{fg text}/@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
 | @{fg fill}+--------------------------------------------+-+@{fg text}
 |             ^
 |             |
 |    Activates the process
 |                            Size (bytes) of files
 +--------------------------- to create



 Menu items:

 @{b}Splitter@{ub}
   Execute <--- Activates the Join/Split process (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + E@{fg text})
   -------
   Chiudi  <--- Closes the window (short key @{fg shine}RAMIGA + C@{fg text})


 @{b}Notes:@{ub}
 The presetted file sizes are:

 ===================================================
  Botton     Bytes   Floppy
 ===================================================
   360 Kb   364032   5.25" DD, 3.5" SD Ms-Dos
