@node "GuiX_UnPacker" "5.5.4 GuiX: UnPacker"


 @{b}Short key: @{fg shine}RAMIGA + 4@{ub}@{fg text}

 UnPacker is a tool that is able to depack all file-disks created with  xFX.
It use the XPK library set and the  unpacked  file  is  overwritten  on  the
original. The supported formats are: XPK, PowerPacker and GZip.



    @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg text}*@{fg fill}|@{fg text} File-Disk UnPacker      @{fg fill}|@{fg text}%@{fg fill}|@{fg text}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}+-+-------------------------+-+-+@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+--------- File-Disk ---------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +------------------++-+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text} Nome |                  ||@{fg shine}^@{fg text}|@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- File-disk name to depack
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}      +------------------++-+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+---------- Progress ---------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+---------------------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}|            @{fg shine}0 %@{fg text}            |@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text} <--- Progress bar
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+------+------+------+------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}0%           50%         100%@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}+-----------------------------+@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
    @{fg fill}|@{fg shine}|@{fg text}+------------+ +------------+@{fg shine}|@{fg fill}|@{fg text}
